  "texts": [
    "For example, if Fe2O 3 with an NER tag of CHM and 'catalyst' with an NER tag of APL are discovered to co-occur in 123 documents, then the triple [Fe 2 O 3, CHM-APL, 'catalyst'] is added to MatKG.",
    "Furthermore, a weight factor of 123 is affixed, thus forming the quartet [Fe 2 O 3, CHM-APL, 'catalyst', 123].",
    "Semantically, this signifies a strong material-application association between Fe2O 3 and 'catalyst'.",
    "Additional analyses from neighboring nodes enable us to deduce that 'catalyst' is indeed an application for Fe2O 3, particularly in the decomposition of sulfuric acid 35.",
    "The intricacies of such connections will be further elucidated in the section on technical validation."
  ],
